{"tid":1511580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法警爆自殺潮今年64死 家屬：職業遭污名化","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T07:47:25.000Z","uid":43556,"like":183,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"71d5c5a324395f0e1795a831c80b085508aecfe9","tid":1511580,"uid":43556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"(星島日報報道)法國警察爆發自殺潮，今年至今已有六十四名警員自殺，單是近日就有八人了結生命，包括三名防暴警察、一名指揮官和一名學堂教官。警察工會說，保護者也需要受到保護，要求當局提供更多的幫助去制止問題。<br />\n<br />\n  自殺的警察來自全國各地，年齡遍布各階層，許多自殺警察遺下了年幼兒女，最近一宗於上周三發生在阿爾代什省。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當局至今未找出接連有警察輕生的具體原因。法國國會在七月公布一項調查，指出警察感到巨大壓力和絕望的原因，包括二〇一五年一月以來的一系列恐怖襲擊，以及去年十一月起連續二十多個周末的「黃背心示威」等，令他們工作過勞。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n  有警察妻子坦言，警察置身當權者和示威者中間，不但要承受壓力與焦慮，還要面對社會上對警察職業的污名化，並批評法國政府不作為，要求得到更多支持。今年四月二十日，「黃背心」第二十三周抗議時，人群中竟出現「警察，去自殺、去自殺」的標語。<br />\n<br />\n  去年另一份報告指出，法國警察自殺率是百分之三十六，比一般自殺率高。法國政府曾於四月底設立自殺預防機構，但效果不佳。法國去年共有三十五名警察自殺，但今年到七月中已突破去年數字，一個月後更增至六十四人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtaousa.com/la/11-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/2465123-%E6%B3%95%E8%AD%A6%E7%88%86%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%BD%AE%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B464%E6%AD%BB+%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%EF%BC%9A%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD%E9%81%AD%E6%B1%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%96/?fromG=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtaousa.com%2Fla%2F11-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F2465123-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B464%25E6%25AD%25BB%2B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%2581%25B7%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%258C%2596%2F%3FfromG%3D1&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=05f6df88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtaousa.com/la/11-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/2465123-%E6%B3%95%E8%AD%A6%E7%88%86%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%BD%AE%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B464%E6%AD%BB+%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%EF%BC%9A%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD%E9%81%AD%E6%B1%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%96/?fromG=1</a>"},{"pid":"a7423b34c890bfd612d459da3e8a4fe4077c86e5","tid":1511580,"uid":59225,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=2a496643\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=434933ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=b449de2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"92a382eca8cc91901b985096746301e4bbc074d0","tid":1511580,"uid":276442,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:41:53.000Z","msg":"香港警察"},{"pid":"b7a22e706f525509e88f6bdd11ab562502d676fa","tid":1511580,"uid":54303,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"92a382eca8cc91901b985096746301e4bbc074d0","tid":1511580,"uid":276442,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:41:53.000Z","msg":"香港警察"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:43:07.000Z","msg":"佢地咁無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c2b4e5ff826e566af7d07fafe98a5ad007d1f4","tid":1511580,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(極