的「黃背心示威」等，令他們工作過勞。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n  有警察妻子坦言，警察置身當權者和示威者中間，不但要承受壓力與焦慮，還要面對社會上對警察職業的污名化，並批評法國政府不作為，要求得到更多支持。今年四月二十日，「黃背心」第二十三周抗議時，人群中竟出現「警察，去自殺、去自殺」的標語。<br />\n<br />\n  去年另一份報告指出，法國警察自殺率是百分之三十六，比一般自殺率高。法國政府曾於四月底設立自殺預防機構，但效果不佳。法國去年共有三十五名警察自殺，但今年到七月中已突破去年數字，一個月後更增至六十四人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtaousa.com/la/11-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/2465123-%E6%B3%95%E8%AD%A6%E7%88%86%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%BD%AE%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B464%E6%AD%BB+%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%EF%BC%9A%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD%E9%81%AD%E6%B1%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%96/?fromG=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtaousa.com%2Fla%2F11-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F2465123-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B464%25E6%25AD%25BB%2B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%2581%25B7%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%258C%2596%2F%3FfromG%3D1&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=05f6df88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtaousa.com/la/11-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/2465123-%E6%B3%95%E8%AD%A6%E7%88%86%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%BD%AE%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B464%E6%AD%BB+%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%EF%BC%9A%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD%E9%81%AD%E6%B1%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%96/?fromG=1</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:49:35.000Z","msg":"無得比較 - 法國警察經歷過槍手恐怖襲擊，出現與壓力有關嘅精神病都唔奇...咁香港班黑犬呢? 可能係賭錢賭到破鳩咗產，搵示威者出氣囉"},{"pid":"be00189d96b97a5767dc0afcd1d51e68c8720bc3","tid":1511580,"uid":272186,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:49:50.000Z","msg":"自殺益哂啲黑警喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個都甲級戰爭犯來"},{"pid":"b01b1c437cc5d06cf2d00ef517ce59d8244c3aa2","tid":1511580,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"良心民族"},{"pid":"f82ca3aad7736039cb7dff1983e25549a9c8c9d3","tid":1511580,"uid":4